      <p>Floating is a deep relaxation experience for the body and mind.</p>
      <p>You lie in a warm bath filled with Epsom salt and water that supports your body and creates the feeling of floating.</p>
      <p>Silence, darkness and weightlessness help you let go of everyday tension.</p>
      <p>Hingamiskeskus offers the floating experience in Tallinn, in cozy and private rooms. The session lasts 60 minutes.</p>
      <h2 class="float-benefits__title">What you feel after floating:</h2>
